comments: waste of money and time. should not be a teacher in any subject. not dedicated to the students and does not follow school policy. syllabus is vague. does not give dates for assignments that are due, is unfamiliar with the text, was late every single day(minus two),if i have learned anything its that her rants are as long as the sin graph STAY AWAY!

Not a good teacher. She is all over the place and will go off about things that make no sense and are completely irrelevant. She lost me sat least 20 times a class, and that was only if she actually showed up. Don\'t take her class.

Often I would show up to class 20 minutes late & the professor still wouldn\'t be there. Rosenberg\'s style is boring and complicated. Math 120 is the easiest class you will ever take... But you won\'t be challenged, and for good students, that will drive you crazy!
Great teacher. Very funny. Easy to talk too. Non bullshet teacher. Took for math30, 100, and now 120. wouldn\'t take anyone else. No attendance kept.
Not helpful. Confusing and unorganized. Often did not show up to class, and never called the office to let someone know. Sometimes sections were taught after the hw for them was due.
